{"tid":2003655,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柏良：建議出現感冒病徵、接受家居檢疫、確診或懷疑個案，及緊密接觸者，或到醫院及老人院等地方人士 唔好戴可重用口罩","createTime":"2020-05-06T03:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T05:24:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fb22a97e85d026893ddbe3fcc5dc5f5db36e3c","tid":2003655,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在電台節目稱，政府的可重用口罩測試結果不錯，布料有一定防水及防細菌，與內衣褲物料差不多，認為可以改善外層顏色，令口罩在觀感上較佳。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良表示，由於可重用口罩只能清洗不可以消毒，建議出現發燒、呼吸道感染病徵、接受家居檢疫、確診或懷疑個案，及緊密接觸者，或到醫院及老人院等高危地方人士，避免配戴，否則可能因口罩表面帶有病毒而提高環境及傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，可重用口罩用6層布料，如配戴時間長，呼吸阻力或會較外科口罩大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2457087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2457087&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=e53a8e3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2457087</a>"},{"pid":"a19ab118bbf11dfae984fa8d3723b73f2b29cb86","tid":2003655,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e1866f071e4c131daae0a85afa386a6ce4a73b8","tid":2003655,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"想問點解唔用得漂白水消毒 ？<br />\n<br />\n消毒咗有乜嘢後果 ？"},{"pid":"372086e10b9c619c26bf2ccc2c77f4c5afceb63d","tid":2003655,"uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:31:49.000Z","msg":"成段剩係留意到 &ldquo;與內衣褲物料差不多&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e51c819115503b6522ee07e763cd9799d36aa57","tid":2003655,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"都幾廢...用清水洗? 咪臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be206f0bcd3cdf583f89fff6391d35376ade4fe2","tid":2003655,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi